title: Open Your Legs for the Military Boys Part 2
description: THE FINAL EXCITING CHAPTER CONTINUESIn the military barracks, I am a slave to Lieutenant Lisa and the whims of her hard-bodied boys. However, they now will subject me to a certain mysterious torture/sexual practice. It is one that has been known to break many prisoners of war.What can it possibly be?And just when I think my life has been all planned out, something unexpected and cruel happens.THIS IS THE LAST CHAPTER OF THE 'OPEN YOUR LEGS' SAGA. FIND OUT IF ANASTASIA GETS EVERYTHING SHE DESERVES.
author: Aphrodite Hunt
